/_agent-tasks/
/LESSONS.md
# Internal dev/audit artifacts — sprint reports, mockups, route sweeps, CI
# sbom output. Ignore everything under artifacts/ EXCEPT the two paths the test
# suite treats as functional fixtures: promise_verify/ (eval contract gated by
# test_promise_v6) and sprint_q3/repro.sh (fs-scan allowlist contract).
/artifacts/*
!/artifacts/promise_verify/
!/artifacts/sprint_q3/
/artifacts/sprint_q3/*
!/artifacts/sprint_q3/repro.sh
# Stale committed benchmark outputs — regenerated by benchmarks.yml / k6-weekly.
/benchmarks/results/
# Founder-only ops tooling (license mint / release / per-customer onboard).
# Leaks our internal release process + key host — never ship to a customer box.
# Kept locally so the founder can still run them; untracked from the repo.
/scripts/release.sh
/scripts/mint_and_email.sh
/scripts/customer_onboard.sh
/scripts/_mint_license.py

# Local-only dev run artifacts (savepoint exclusions — never committed)
.localrun/
**/.localrun/
core/landing/.localrun_frontend.sh
core/landing/.localrun_*.mjs
*.bak
.env.bak.*
infra/*.bak
